  "detailed_description": "Set in an Apocalyptic World, you play as a renegade with incredible endurance and speed, demolishing enemies with arcade like weapons.<br>TileDynasty is an FPS Arena, where Players can work together against AI Enemies or go head-to-head accomplishing objectives within each game mode.<br><br><br>WEAPONS<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">GRENADE LAUNCHER</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">RIFLE</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">MACHINE GUN</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">ROCKET LAUNCHER</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">PORTER GUN</ul><br>MOVEMENT: Designed for fluid-like motion, coupled with Wall Movement, use multiple approaches to get to different platforms to your strategy! <br><br>LEVELS: Maps will be designed to tailor to the 'Arcade-Feel' of the game<br><br>CURRENT MODES:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">SEARCH AND RESCUE: Locate the hostages in each map and escort them back to the rescue zone, and defend the hostages from the enemy</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">TEAM DEATH MATCH: Head-To-Head online with friends or against AI</ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Set in an Apocalyptic World, you play as a renegade with incredible endurance and speed, demolishing enemies with arcade like weapons.<br>TileDynasty is an FPS Arena, where Players can work together against AI Enemies or go head-to-head accomplishing objectives within each game mode.<br><br><br>WEAPONS<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">GRENADE LAUNCHER</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">RIFLE</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">MACHINE GUN</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">ROCKET LAUNCHER</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">PORTER GUN</ul><br>MOVEMENT: Designed for fluid-like motion, coupled with Wall Movement, use multiple approaches to get to different platforms to your strategy! <br><br>LEVELS: Maps will be designed to tailor to the 'Arcade-Feel' of the game<br><br>CURRENT MODES:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">SEARCH AND RESCUE: Locate the hostages in each map and escort them back to the rescue zone, and defend the hostages from the enemy</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">TEAM DEATH MATCH: Head-To-Head online with friends or against AI</ul>",
